visualization

d1 %>% 
  mutate(Model = fct_relevel(Model, c("LLaMA","SERAC","ROME","IKE","ReMaKE-zero","ReMaKE-few-mono","ReMaKE-few-bi" ))) %>% 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_path(mapping = aes(y =  Model, x = Value, color = Language, group = Language), linewidth = 1.25, alpha = .3) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(y =  Model, x = Value, color = Language)) +
  facet_wrap(Metric ~ .) +
  theme_ggdist()

unique(d1$Language)
##  [1] "EN" "CS" "DE" "NL" "ES" "FR" "PT" "RU" "TH" "TR" "VI" "ZH"
scale_color_model = \(...) scale_color_manual(...,
                                              values = c("LLaMA" = '#999999',
                                                         "ROME" = '#7fa187',
                                                         "SERAC" = '#8c7d99',
                                                         'IKE' = '#7f99a1',
                                                         'ReMaKE-zero' = '#e87654',
                                                         "ReMaKE-few-mono" = '#e6a607',
                                                         "ReMaKE-few-bi" =  '#ff3a00'),
                                              aesthetics = c("color", "fill"))
p1 <- d1 %>% 
  mutate(Model = fct_relevel(Model, c("LLaMA","SERAC","ROME","IKE","ReMaKE-zero","ReMaKE-few-mono","ReMaKE-few-bi" ))) %>% 
  mutate(Language = fct_relevel(Language, c("EN","CS", "DE", "NL", "ES", "FR" ,"PT", "RU", "TH", "TR", "VI" ,"ZH"))) %>% 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_path(mapping = aes(y =  Language, x = Value, color = Model, group = Model), linewidth = 1.25, alpha = .3) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(y =  Language, x = Value, color = Model)) +
  facet_wrap(Metric ~ .) +
  scale_color_model() + xlab('') + ggtitle('A. blah blah') + 
  theme_ggdist() +
  theme(legend.position = 'bottom')

p1

p2 <- d2 %>% 
  mutate(Model = fct_relevel(Model, c("LLaMA","SERAC","ROME","IKE","ReMaKE-zero","ReMaKE-few-mono","ReMaKE-few-bi" ))) %>% 
  mutate(Language = fct_relevel(Language, c("CS", "DE", "NL", "ES", "FR" ,"PT", "RU", "TH", "TR", "VI" ,"ZH"))) %>% 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_path(mapping = aes(y =  Language, x = Value, color = Model, group = Model), linewidth = 1.25, alpha = .3) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(y =  Language, x = Value, color = Model)) +
  facet_wrap(Metric ~ .) +
  scale_color_model() + xlab('') + ggtitle('B. blah blah') + 
  theme_ggdist() +
  theme(legend.position = 'bottom')

p2
